        <num>CC 2442</num>
        <heading>2442.  Recordation of sale of immovable to affect third persons</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2442.  Recordation of sale of immovable to affect third persons
The parties to an act of sale or promise of sale of immovable property are bound from
the time that the act is made, but such an act is not effective against third persons until it is
filed for registry according to the laws of registry.</p>
        </content>
